Step 1:
mkdir -p ~/.local/share/fonts
cd ~/.local/share/fonts
curl -fLo "JetBrainsMono.zip" https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/releases/tag/v3.3.0/FiraCode.zip
unzip JetBrainsmono.zip
rm JetBrainsMono.zip
or 
Goto my directory copy /.local/share/fonts/JetBrainsMono folder to your /.local/share/fonts folder if you dont have font folder crate it 
mkdir fonts

Step 2:
after downloading rfresh chache for xterm terminal 
fc-cache -fv

Step 3:
Crate or open ~/.Xresources and add this taxt 
XTerm*faceName: JetBrainsMono Nerd Font
XTerm*faceSize: 12

Step:4 Reset(Close/Open) your terminal
